{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1183580/extras/TA_Header_TheGame_EN_(600_x_146).png?t=1715673995\" /><br><br>Welcome to a world where magic and technology go hand in hand. In Terra Alia, every nation has its own rules for using magic, as it is a common part of this world. To avoid conflicts, these nations have come together to oversee magic use in their lands. <br><br>The first rule they created is learning the local language before you can start developing your magical abilities.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1183580/extras/TA_Steam_theworld_GIF.gif?t=1715673995\" /><br><br>Your adventure begins in your homeland, just after completing your studies at one of Terra Alia's most renowned magic academies. Professor Esperanto, your esteemed mentor, has invited you to continue studies abroad in her exclusive technomancy program. Upon your arrival, you\u2019ve found that the professor has gone missing! What mischievous force could be behind her disappearance? To solve this riddle, you'll need to unlock your magical abilities, but you've got to learn the local language first.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1183580/extras/puzzle.gif?t=1715673995\" /><br><br>Choose your target language, and expand your vocabulary while confronting mythical creatures, rogue androids, and many other challenges as you journey through the magical realm of Terra Alia!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1183580/extras/TA_Header_Features_EN_(600_x_146).png?t=1715673995\" /><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Master a vocabulary of hundreds of words in 10 different languages!<br></li><li>Complete quest lines filled with gripping stories while solving challenging puzzles!<br></li><li>Cast powerful spells as you battle enemies in a dynamic turn-based combat system.<br></li><li>Level up and equip your character with increasingly more powerful abilities and items.<br></li><li>Unravel a mystery that threatens all of Terra Alia by following clues and hints.</li></ul>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Citizen of Terra Alia","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1183580/edc75390eff6fdee41e1e23470e6144c743e5bb2.jpg"},{"name":"Bilingual","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1183580/bcb1518630faa56eac4040de591042d0f676e54e.jpg"},{"name":"Trilingual","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1183580/4422dcabd4d363a255c14f1da8a7ea5d80e04cb4.jpg"},{"name":"Polyglot","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1183580/ef801ea7483bb3570c2ea90c24bc03377d9e0669.jpg"},{"name":"Tower of Babel","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1183580/9e2a58dcdc876f4db26bf81b118c65e497723bf2.jpg"},{"name":"Apprentice","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1183580/440718989c91603f11958e855074f2beb34006f6.jpg"},{"name":"Mage","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1183580/e9821e982ee941071b9a7644e91800128d256ef9.jpg"},{"name":"Archmage","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1183580/86b9c4435365d57530c07a9b8dd4264c56c4dc34.jpg"},{"name":"Talented","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1183580/20607182a76991066cba6f792145a8862db0c9f6.jpg"},{"name":"Septimus","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1183580/1eb69aa9ae21a01970739b7493b2fb5d6371ae04.jpg"}],"total":21},"background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1183580/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1715673995","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1183580/page.bg.jpg?t=1715673995","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1183580/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1715673995","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1183580/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1715673995","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Steam Achievements","id":22},{"description":"Family Sharing","id":62}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"detailed_description":"<h1>Join Our Discord</h1><p><br><br>Join the magic of our official Terra Alia Discord server! Engage with others, share your progress and unravel the mystery of this amazing new world!<br><br>Games are best when played with others! Join our Discord server for the latest news, special events and exclusive access to player support for when spells go awry!<br><br><br>Join our community on Discord to keep in touch, access support, and stay up to date on all things Terra Alia!</p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1183580/extras/TA_Header_TheGame_EN_(600_x_146).png?t=1715673995\" /><br><br>Welcome to a world where magic and technology go hand in hand. In Terra Alia, every nation has its own rules for using magic, as it is a common part of this world. To avoid conflicts, these nations have come together to oversee magic use in their lands. <br><br>The first rule they created is learning the local language before you can start developing your magical abilities.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1183580/extras/TA_Steam_theworld_GIF.gif?t=1715673995\" /><br><br>Your adventure begins in your homeland, just after completing your studies at one of Terra Alia's most renowned magic academies. Professor Esperanto, your esteemed mentor, has invited you to continue studies abroad in her exclusive technomancy program. Upon your arrival, you\u2019ve found that the professor has gone missing! What mischievous force could be behind her disappearance? To solve this riddle, you'll need to unlock your magical abilities, but you've got to learn the local language first.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1183580/extras/puzzle.gif?t=1715673995\" /><br><br>Choose your target language, and expand your vocabulary while confronting mythical creatures, rogue androids, and many other challenges as you journey through the magical realm of Terra Alia!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1183580/extras/TA_Header_Features_EN_(600_x_146).png?t=1715673995\" /><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Master a vocabulary of hundreds of words in 10 different languages!<br></li><li>Complete quest lines filled with gripping stories while solving challenging puzzles!<br></li><li>Cast powerful spells as you battle enemies in a dynamic turn-based combat system.<br></li><li>Level up and equip your character with increasingly more powerful abilities and items.<br></li><li>Unravel a mystery that threatens all of Terra Alia by following clues and hints.</li></ul>","developers":["30 Parallel"],"genres":[{"description":"Adventure","id":"25"},{"description":"Indie","id":"23"},{"description":"RPG","id":"3"}],"header_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1183580/header.jpg?t=1715673995","is_free":false,"linux_requirements":{"minimum":"<strong>Minimum:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"></ul>","recommended":"<strong>Recommended:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"></ul>"},"mac_requirements":{"minimum":"<strong>Minimum:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"></ul>","recommended":"<strong>Recommended:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"></ul>"},"movies":[{"highlight":true,"id":256797343,"mp4":{"480":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/256797343/movie480.mp4?t=